      "title": "British MP Calls For International Arrest Warrant Against Gotabaya Rajapaksa",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "New Delhi: Sir Ed Davey, the chief of the Liberal Democrats, has demanded that a global arrest warrant ought to be issued in opposition to Sri Lanka President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and his \u201ccronies\u201d.",
        "\u201cThe horrible state of affairs in Sri Lanka has been caused by the corruption of the Rajapaksa Authorities, tax cuts, skyrocketing defence expenditure and draconian police powers,\u201d he was quoted by the media.",
        "Talking within the Home of Commons, Davey instructed that the UK works with worldwide companions for a full financial and political resolution to \u201cassist the democrats in Sri Lanka,\u201d which incorporates the issuance of an arrest warrant.",
        "British MP Calls For International Arrest Warrant Against Gotabaya Rajapaksa",
        "Russia \u201cResponsible\u201d For Ongoing Crisis In Sri Lanka: Ukraine\u2019s Zelensky",
        "Army empowered to use force to protect lives & state property",
